%2FZRZT8Zu.jpg&h=af97adff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《堅信愛會贏》由舒楠作曲，廣東話版由陳星、彭凱滔填詞，<span style=\"color: red;\">邀請了港澳台多位歌手藝人演唱，包括任達華、鍾鎮濤、惠英紅、莫華倫、劉愷威、陳偉霆、張衛健、馬國明、郭采潔、Solar等</span>，他們又在歌曲中段，隔空為武漢加油，用音樂為大家打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">大台廣告時段成首播曬，真係好俾面央視，唔播都唔得啦，無乜廣告用嚟攝時間都要嘅</span><br />\n<br />\n唱完真係可以抗疫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲攪埋啲咁嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇佢啲咩&ldquo;港澳台明星&rdquo;就知道廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c3500092bffc92fa60381a4212a2a7ea389361","tid":1883053,"uid":150483,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:16:03.000Z","msg":"冇廣告先播，如果將佢改到好似肥媽咁<br />\n包保永遠唔再播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c73048f1d0ad4aac1bdf6443b8d1eef241464f","tid":1883053,"uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0c3500092bffc92fa60381a4212a2a7ea389361","tid":1883053,"uid":150483,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:16:03.000Z","msg":"冇廣告先播，如果將佢改到好似肥媽咁<br />\n包保永遠唔再播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"呀&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946c7a05b96a624cb58edf196025975a911fedd1","tid":1883053,"uid":225130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:17:41.000Z","msg":"郭采潔 台灣都撈唔掂"},{"pid":"0eb5503ea3f539389a486c3b9adc68d5819f01e6","tid":1883053,"uid":127413,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:18:42.000Z","msg":"好撚難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c039a536bbd6f353fd730102f87d94b2d39cab","tid":1883053,"uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"946c7a05b96a624cb58edf196025975a911fedd1","tid":1883053,"uid":225130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score